cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use QIL in academic work, please cite both the software and the accompanying manuscript."
title: "QIL — Quaternionic Invariant Laboratory"
abstract: >-
  An open-source, exact-arithmetic research framework in Rust for the study of
  non-commutative quaternionic invariants of 3-SAT and the structural collapse
  mechanisms of Geometric Complexity Theory: the Intrinsic Bipartite Gauge
  Collapse and the Extrinsic Terminal Abelianization.
type: software
