date-released: "2026-07-02"
license: "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords:
  - quaternion
  - non-commutative algebra
  - geometric complexity theory
  - exact arithmetic
  - 3-SAT
  - hypergraph
repository-code: "https://github.com/mauramyrez11/QIL-Research-Framework"
